{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1927,"text":"It is almost the end of the winter,"},{"time":4881,"text":"and you've woken up to a cold house,"},{"time":7476,"text":"which is weird, because\nyou left the heater on all night."},{"time":12124,"text":"You turn on the light."},{"time":13449,"text":"It's not working."},{"time":15252,"text":"Actually, the coffee maker, the TV --\nnone of them are working."},{"time":21249,"text":"Life outside also seems to have stopped."},{"time":24796,"text":"There are no schools,"},{"time":26648,"text":"most of the businesses are shut,"},{"time":28913,"text":"and there are no working trains."},{"time":31852,"text":"This is not the opening scene\nof a zombie apocalypse movie."}]},{"cues":[{"time":36332,"text":"This is what happened in March 1989\nin the Canadian province of Quebec,"},{"time":42268,"text":"when the power grid lost power."},{"time":45523,"text":"The culprit?"},{"time":47106,"text":"A solar storm."}]},{"cues":[{"time":49551,"text":"Solar storms are giant clouds of particles"},{"time":52638,"text":"escaping from the Sun from time to time,"},{"time":54940,"text":"and a constant reminder that we live\nin the neighborhood of an active star."},{"time":61157,"text":"And I, as a solar physicist,"},{"time":63789,"text":"I have a tremendous chance\nto study these solar storms."},{"time":67533,"text":"But you see, \"solar storm chaser\""},{"time":70278,"text":"is not just a cool title."},{"time":72799,"text":"My research helps to understand\nwhere they come from,"},{"time":76459,"text":"how they behave"},{"time":77927,"text":"and, in the long run,"},{"time":79126,"text":"aims to mitigate their effects\non human societies,"},{"time":82148,"text":"which I'll get to in a second."}]},{"cues":[{"time":85106,"text":"At the beginning of the space\nexploration age 50 years ago only,"},{"time":90674,"text":"the probes we sent in space"},{"time":92856,"text":"revealed that the planets\nin our Solar System"},{"time":95694,"text":"constantly bathe in a stream of particles\nthat are coming from the Sun"},{"time":100168,"text":"and that we call the solar wind."},{"time":103722,"text":"And in the same way that global wind\npatterns here on Earth"},{"time":107363,"text":"can be affected by hurricanes,"},{"time":109585,"text":"the solar wind is sometimes\naffected by solar storms"},{"time":113370,"text":"that I like to call \"space hurricanes.\""},{"time":117687,"text":"When they arrive at planets,"},{"time":119664,"text":"they can perturb the space environment,"},{"time":121913,"text":"which in turn creates\nthe northern or southern lights,"},{"time":125222,"text":"for example, here on Earth,"},{"time":127434,"text":"but also Saturn"},{"time":129953,"text":"and also Jupiter."}]},{"cues":[{"time":133151,"text":"Luckily, here on Earth,"},{"time":135863,"text":"we are protected\nby our planet's natural shield,"},{"time":138978,"text":"a magnetic bubble that we call\nthe magnetosphere"},{"time":142113,"text":"and that you can see here\non the right side."},{"time":145281,"text":"Nonetheless, solar storms\ncan still be responsible"},{"time":148553,"text":"for disrupting satellite\ntelecommunications and operations,"},{"time":153191,"text":"for disrupting navigation\nsystems, such as GPS,"},{"time":156820,"text":"as well as electric power transmission."},{"time":159895,"text":"All of these are technologies\non which us humans rely more and more."},{"time":166420,"text":"I mean, imagine if you woke up tomorrow\nwithout a working cell phone --"},{"time":171692,"text":"no internet on it,"},{"time":173269,"text":"which means no social media."},{"time":175799,"text":"I mean, to me that would be worse\nthan the zombie apocalypse."}]},{"cues":[{"time":178747,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":180605,"text":"By constantly monitoring the Sun, though,"},{"time":182724,"text":"we now know where\nthe solar storms come from."},{"time":185753,"text":"They come from regions of the Sun"},{"time":187722,"text":"where a tremendous amount\nof energy is being stored."},{"time":191038,"text":"You have an example here,"},{"time":192574,"text":"as a complex structure\nhanging above the solar surface,"},{"time":196408,"text":"just on the verge of erupting."},{"time":199877,"text":"Unfortunately, we cannot send probes"},{"time":202787,"text":"in the scorching hot\natmosphere of the Sun,"},{"time":206230,"text":"where temperatures can rise\nup to around 10 million degrees Kelvin."},{"time":212227,"text":"So what I do is I use computer simulations"},{"time":216462,"text":"in order to analyze but also to predict\nthe behavior of these storms"},{"time":221319,"text":"when they're just born at the Sun."}]},{"cues":[{"time":225421,"text":"This is only one part\nof the story, though."},{"time":229486,"text":"When these solar storms\nare moving in space,"},{"time":233368,"text":"some of them will inevitably\nencounter space probes"},{"time":236998,"text":"that we humans have sent\nin order to explore other worlds."},{"time":242105,"text":"What I mean by other worlds is,\nfor example, planets,"},{"time":244962,"text":"such as Venus or Mercury,"},{"time":247086,"text":"but also objects, such as comets."},{"time":250584,"text":"And while these space probes\nhave been made"},{"time":253194,"text":"for different scientific endeavors,"},{"time":255929,"text":"they can also act like tiny\ncosmic meteorological stations"},{"time":261090,"text":"and monitor the evolution\nof these space storms."},{"time":264979,"text":"So I, with a group of researchers,\ngather and analyze this data"},{"time":270338,"text":"coming from different\nlocations of the Solar System."},{"time":273411,"text":"And by doing so, my research\nshows that, actually,"},{"time":276751,"text":"solar storms have a generic shape,"},{"time":278863,"text":"and that this shape evolves\nas solar storms move away from the Sun."},{"time":283392,"text":"And you know what?"},{"time":284571,"text":"This is key for building tools\nto predict space weather."}]},{"cues":[{"time":291420,"text":"I would like to leave you\nwith this beautiful image."},{"time":294529,"text":"This is us here on Earth,"},{"time":297692,"text":"this pale blue dot."},{"time":299736,"text":"And while I study the Sun\nand its storms every day,"},{"time":303424,"text":"I will always have a deep love\nfor this beautiful planet --"},{"time":308076,"text":"a pale blue dot indeed,"},{"time":309491,"text":"but a pale blue dot\nwith an invisible magnetic shield"},{"time":313399,"text":"that helps to protect us."}]},{"cues":[{"time":315629,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":316959,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}